  Memory Usage: 33.2 MB (min: 32.5, max: 33.2, avg: 32.8)
  CPU Time: 1245.30 ms (min: 0.00, max: 1245.30, avg: 622.65)
  Parse Time: 5.20 ms (min: 2.10, max: 5.20, avg: 3.65)
